TITLE: JSON Processing Performance Impact Example
DESCRIPTION: Shows how large JSON operations can block the Event Loop. Creates an exponentially growing object and measures time taken for stringify, indexOf, and parse operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/learn/asynchronous-work/dont-block-the-event-loop.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

