TITLE: Implementing O(nÂ²) Complexity Callback in Express.js
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates an O(nÂ²) complexity callback in an Express.js route handler. The execution time grows quadratically with the input parameter n, making it more likely to block the Event Loop for even moderately large values of n.
