TITLE: Implementing Custom _read Method (CJS)
DESCRIPTION: Provides an example of a custom Readable stream class 'MyStream' which overrides the '_read' method. Uses 'setImmediate' to asynchronously push data, emitting 'null' to signify stream end after 5 pushes. Designed for small buffer sizes and demonstrating readable event triggering frequency.
