DESCRIPTION: This commit marks the `test-watch-mode-inspect` test as flaky. This indicates that the test is known to fail intermittently due to reasons unrelated to code correctness. Marking tests as flaky allows the test suite to continue running without being blocked by non-deterministic failures.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v18.19.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_31



