TITLE: Promise-based File Reading with util.promisify
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to convert callback-based Node.js APIs into Promise-based ones using the new util.promisify() utility function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v8.0.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const fs = require('fs');
const util = require('util');

const readfile = util.promisify(fs.readFile);

readfile('/some/file')
  .then(data => {
    /** ... **/
  })
  .catch(err => {
    /** ... **/
  });
```

