TITLE: Release Commit Changes in Node.js v23.7.0
DESCRIPTION: A list of commit hashes and their corresponding changes for Node.js version 23.7.0, including updates to crypto, fs, module, sqlite, src, and test_runner components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v23.7.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
[[`36dd9ecc41`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/36dd9ecc41)] - **crypto**: update root certificates to NSS 3.107
[[`9414d3cbf1`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/9414d3cbf1)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **fs**: allow `exclude` option in globs to accept glob patterns
[[`9c5c3b3115`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/9c5c3b3115)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **module**: add ERR_UNSUPPORTED_TYPESCRIPT_SYNTAX
[[`1e201fd5fd`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/1e201fd5fd)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **sqlite**: support TypedArray and DataView in `StatementSync`
[[`48c813fb67`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/48c813fb67)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **src**: add --disable-sigusr1 to prevent signal i/o thread
[[`cf16123785`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/cf16123785)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **src,worker**: add isInternalWorker
[[`13bdd9c961`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/13bdd9c961)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **test_runner**: add TestContext.prototype.waitFor()
[[`00a1943858`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/00a1943858)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **test_runner**: add t.assert.fileSnapshot()
[[`3143566045`](https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/3143566045)] - **(SEMVER-MINOR)** **test_runner**: add assert.register() API
```

