TITLE: Using v8.startupSnapshot API for Snapshots in Node.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet explains how to utilize the `v8.startupSnapshot` API to define an entry point when building a snapshot. This approach allows users to eliminate the need for an additional entry script during deserialization, enhancing efficiency.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v18.8.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
echo "require('v8').startupSnapshot.setDeserializeMainFunction(() => console.log('I am from the snapshot'))" > snapshot.js
node --snapshot-blob snapshot.blob --build-snapshot snapshot.js
node --snapshot-blob snapshot.blob
# => I am from the snapshot
```

