TITLE: Updating stream behavior in Node.js
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet updates the stream module to support dispose in writable streams and fixes issues with stream pausing and destruction.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v22.4.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
**stream**: support dispose in writable (Benjamin Gruenbaum) [#48547](https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/48547)
**stream**: callback should be called when pendingcb is 0 (jakecastelli) [#53438](https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/53438)
**stream**: make sure \_destroy is called (jakecastelli) [#53213](https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/53213)
**stream**: prevent stream unexpected pause when highWaterMark set to 0 (jakecastelli) [#53261](https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/53261)
```

