TITLE: Zero Delay setTimeout in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the behavior of setTimeout with a zero delay, which executes the callback as soon as possible after the current function execution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/learn/asynchronous-work/discover-javascript-timers.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
setTimeout(() => {
  console.log('after ');
}, 0);

console.log(' before ');
```

