TITLE: Test Runner and Stream Improvements
DESCRIPTION: Adds new features to test runner including suite() function, forced exit support, and test:complete event. Implements typed array support in streams and adds new utility functions for text styling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v22.0.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_12



----------------------------------------

TITLE: Exposing Keylog Event on TLSSocket in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This commit adds a new 'keylog' event to the TLSSocket class. This event provides access to key material for TLS connections, which can be useful for debugging and security analysis.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v12.3.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
tlsSocket.on('keylog', (line) => {
  console.log(line);
});
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Installing the stackvis Tool
DESCRIPTION: Command to globally install the stackvis npm package, which is used to transform DTrace output into SVG flame graphs for visualizing performance data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/uncategorized/profiling-node-js.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install -g stackvis
```

