TITLE: Add SkipIfInspectorDisabled to Debugger PID Test
DESCRIPTION: This snippet adds a condition to skip the debugger PID test when the inspector is disabled, enhancing the test suite's reliability by ensuring that it only runs under proper conditions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v8.0.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_66

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// Adding skip condition for inspector
if (!isInspectorEnabled()) {
    skip('Inspector is disabled');
}

```

