TITLE: Installing Node.js using nvm
DESCRIPTION: Commands for installing and managing Node.js versions using nvm (Node Version Manager).
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/es/download/package-manager/all.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
env VERSION=`python tools/getnodeversion.py` make install DESTDIR=`nvm_version_path v$VERSION` PREFIX=""
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
nvm use 8
```

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
nvm uninstall 8
```

