TITLE: N-API Reuse napi_env Between Modules
DESCRIPTION: This commit modifies the N-API to reuse `napi_env` between modules. This optimization reduces overhead and improves performance when loading and using multiple native addons. This can lead to significant performance improvements in applications that rely heavily on native addons.
