TITLE: Fixing Slowloris HTTP Headers in Node.js v6.15.1
DESCRIPTION: Commit reference that fixes the backport of the Slowloris headers vulnerability (CVE-2018-12122) in Node.js. The previous implementation in v6.15.0 incorrectly applied headers timeout to entire keep-alive HTTP sessions.
