TITLE: Replacing FromJust() with Check() in Node.js C++ Source
DESCRIPTION: This commit replaces the use of FromJust() with Check() where possible in the Node.js C++ source code. This change likely improves error handling and type safety.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v12.0.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: C++
CODE:
```
// Example of replacing FromJust() with Check()
// Before:
int value = someHandle->IntegerValue(context).FromJust();

// After:
int value;
if (!someHandle->IntegerValue(context).To(&value)) {
  return;
}
```

