TITLE: VM API Memory Management Improvements
DESCRIPTION: Rework of memory management in VM APIs supporting importModuleDynamically, addressing memory leaks and use-after-free issues in VM Script, compileFunction, SyntheticModule, and SourceTextModule.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nodejs/nodejs.org/blob/main/apps/site/pages/en/blog/release/v20.8.0.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const vm = require('vm');

// Fixed memory management in VM APIs
const script = new vm.Script(code, {
  importModuleDynamically: specifier => import(specifier)
});

const module = new vm.SourceTextModule(code, {
  importModuleDynamically: specifier => import(specifier)
});
```

